{"tid":228812,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[四年一度] 正字 鍾意定中意？","createTime":"2017-05-04T07:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T08:45:53.000Z","uid":50020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f159edf87d7c8ade847ad2238e71a2cc08d7923","tid":228812,"uid":50020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:27:29.000Z","msg":"又來到四年一度既世界正字大賽<br />\n話說小弟剛才喺某個post睇到d嘢<br />\n有位紅字嘅絲定巴講左中意呢個詞語<br />\n然後仲信心十足咁叫人唔好中佢娘親，話中意先係正字<br />\n其他巴絲又真係無人中佢老母喎&hellip;搞到我都淆淆地<br />\n<br />\n一百萬嘅問題來啦！<br />\n到底中意定鍾意先係正字呢？<br />\n<br />\n利申：文盲"},{"pid":"884e90a86533f6bbf913e9f0415e93089568c452","tid":228812,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:28:17.000Z","msg":"中二<br />\n中二病"},{"pid":"74cbd9e078a85e80bcfd9a1c0b65b5212c6547db","tid":228812,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:28:22.000Z","msg":"一定係中意"},{"pid":"f1f799f21f5990836a1a0b0b757893058ef61987","tid":228812,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:28:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/58528\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/58528</a>"},{"pid":"70f564f4dbe3bc284f02be12947e03946ffdb742","tid":228812,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:29:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/58303/page/2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/58303/page/2</a>"},{"pid":"7296c4ad7c72ec4a10af848eeb781b2e454f52d1","tid":228812,"uid":50020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/58528\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/58528</a></blockquote><br />\n引用例子--會員&quot;炭鹼化合物&quot;<br />\n[[ 學術台大撚把迷信嘅中醫撚<br />\n<br />\n最中意話中醫有效但又拎唔出數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPs. 咪中我老母，呢個先係正字 ]]<br />\n<br />\n睇完之前個post<br />\n我覺得呢d情況用中意應該無問題"},{"pid":"ab732d83b97cd4c005554aac3374a249d431b36e","tid":228812,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:50:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個中字如果解作合意時要讀第三聲zung3/jung3。<br />\n好似<br />\n睇中(zung3/jung3)<br />\n中(zung3/jung3)獎<br />\n正中(zung3/jung3)下懷<br />\n<br />\n中字喺解位置先會讀第一聲zung1/jung1。<br />\n好似<br />\n中(zung1/jung1)間<br />\n中(zung1/jung1)學<br />\n萬中(zung1/jung1)無一<br />\n<br />\n所以中意要讀第三聲中(zung3/jung3)意（即「眾意」），都唔係廣東話普遍嘅發音，所以我偏向鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁意思上兩隻字係咪有差異<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中(zung3/jung3)意就係字面解合自己嘅心意<br />\n鍾(zung1/jung1)意就係鍾愛嘅心意<br />\n<br />\n中(zung1/jung1)就係中間嘅心意啩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但係譬如「我中（zung3／jung3）意你」<br />\n<br />\n理應解作「我契合你的心意」<br />\n<br />\n言則賓主相換<br />\n<br />\n無論音義<br />\n<br />\n皆與我等口語日常用法有所偏離<br />\n<br />\n故鄙人與絲打所見略同<br />\n<br />\n「鍾意」較中我意</blockquote>"},{"pid":"410361a3bdc595f001f3b27e2789785d5db735c4","tid":228812,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T07:51:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/58528\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/58528</a></blockquote><br />\n引用例子--會員&quot;炭鹼化合物&quot;<br />\n[[ 學術台大撚把迷信嘅中醫撚<br />\n<br />\n最中意話中醫有效但又拎唔出數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPs. 咪中我老母，呢個先係正字 ]]<br />\n<br />\n睇完之前個post<br />\n我覺得呢d情況用中意應該無問題</blockquote><br />\n諗清楚主語同賓語係咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92e56e81e1e98d0b0d3b489e793919073ea4ba4","tid":228812,"uid":16472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:05:24.000Z","msg":"宗義"},{"pid":"bba49325d1b023bf826fc32d450efc913cb46225","tid":228812,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T08:07:22.000Z","msg":"問問Ben sir啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor